{"tid":547014,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Youtuber鄭金鈴係咪新移民既表表者之真相(3)","createTime":"2018-02-01T04:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T15:34:23.000Z","uid":84308,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ce21f8d529364f2e80b12b3238b7acaa1b7cc94d","tid":547014,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"見未有人開post <br />\n大家繼續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>15歲賣任天堂週邊<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">老翻</span>帽賣到出左名<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/210851_67563dea8a97aa681549f6b1f37af49b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F210851_67563dea8a97aa681549f6b1f37af49b.png&h=3eea413f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上埋星期日檔案繼續感動全港市民<br />\n等大家知道活係貧窮線下既孩子有幾苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好彩之後ling ling識左個男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲推介左佢去電台做dj<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/26/231816_b9764986a547e475afeb9b1fdb7c45bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F231816_b9764986a547e475afeb9b1fdb7c45bf.png&h=a1fe978d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n憑自己既本事攞老綜攞到中學grad trip去歐洲<br />\n幾多香港學生連長洲做grad trip都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鈴鈴真係好有本事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入到大學緊係第一時間溝反條有錢仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲參選過face既u花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/205311_fb3da81a585f6bcc67a7198770462c8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F205311_fb3da81a585f6bcc67a7198770462c8c.png&h=64732b68&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/26/232643_2e32e8aaf05361b89cd64a0796a3aee8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F232643_2e32e8aaf05361b89cd64a0796a3aee8.png&h=41261585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攞完哂香港資源就拍拍籮柚走人<br />\n搬左去泡國做韓國通kol拍下片<br />\n仲開左間ig shop幫大家代購韓國好物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連beauty beggar都做埋<br />\n有時會有啲翻譯job接下<br />\n可以溝下韓仔比仔圍又有得攬頭攬頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/135654_f5fc146d8ebd71b4782abd946034fa0a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F135654_f5fc146d8ebd71b4782abd946034fa0a.png&h=bba497ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/26/234855_c58cf5411ca5725abd0f3fcc6b1892cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F234855_c58cf5411ca5725abd0f3fcc6b1892cc.png&h=e33ab507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寓工作於娛樂 日日濕住揾銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n年薪百萬不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/204534_478af73bf16fa45e4f219aa6e91002c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F204534_478af73bf16fa45e4f219aa6e91002c7.png&h=c385bd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有蝗版李聖經之稱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/205530_560d268429a15ba404312c6d301ef5bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F205530_560d268429a15ba404312c6d301ef5bd.png&h=82d9e58d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/210554_bca8ea8c61015cb6151749f02eb91852.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F210554_bca8ea8c61015cb6151749f02eb91852.png&h=418e7b49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/205531_644df3b5a80e62cfd5e841e6147047e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F205531_644df3b5a80e62cfd5e841e6147047e3.png&h=c8336e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金鈴真係新移民典範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人生勝利組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港好多資源培育各位好似金ling咁力爭上游<br />\n既同胞，支持更多年輕內地人才落黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望內地來港既小朋友都可以打出一片天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過最近金ling既努力竟然比人抄襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竟然抄人沖涼 咁無恥都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/26/235447_de1d389ffb8a80f3a8ddb92b61e0599e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F26%2F235447_de1d389ffb8a80f3a8ddb92b61e0599e.png&h=8acd8982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nling係story回應話比人抄片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/195131_c66f20eceb0f36132d269cd8c7171512.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F195131_c66f20eceb0f36132d269cd8c7171512.png&h=dbd5e947&s={SIZE}\" /> 小金所指既物以類聚係Mao同Mira<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎拍韓國生活既youtube清泉真係得返金ling<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但竟然有人就抄片事件攞當年賣帽抽秤金ling<br />\n搞到鄭金鈴嬲嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/201629_bae2dacd54740dfc5bb7357b277fcf8f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F201629_bae2dacd54740dfc5bb7357b277fcf8f.png&h=ff25cd04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金ling由細到大咁努力向上爬，風光背後既辛酸有無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無做好功課就亂攻擊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抹煞人地多年黎既努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要為我地既同胞鈴鈴攞返個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對抄襲，尊重知識產權！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼續推到Maomao同Mario出黎同金鈴道歉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正評支持金鈴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/001750_468e333b1214d50fc9b59c23f99536ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F001750_468e333b1214d50fc9b59c23f99536ba.png&h=128b5c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/001644_2c1d4897df8c9bd4d7d8d41ae8be3179.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F001644_2c1d4897df8c9bd4d7d8d41ae8be3179.png&h=e5017f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做個summary先<br />\n1. 綜援賣帽少女單嘢係明報報先嘅，但google一搵原來係鄭金鈴自己報料俾各大傳媒去報佢，但得明報落搭<br />\n2. 起咗佢成個Xanga出嚟，一路都係形象百變，受訪前係曲髮，上報喇就整返個負厘子扮乖女<br />\n3. 大陸有間大屋，不時返上去玩，天水圍間公屋又闊落，爽歪歪<br />\n4. 上咗集鏗鏘集定星期X檔案，加埋個Blog，睇到佢生活都幾富泰，平時飯餸又魚又鴨，兩部數碼相機，電子琴小提琴，新嘅plasma電視，NSD，上面巴打話有Xbob，你話唔有錢都OK，但話拎綜援赤貧就有點誇囉<br />\n5. 喺forum賣老翻Anna Siu銀包，喺學校又幫同學燒mp3落CD，逐隻歌計錢<br />\n6. 點解第一頁話果陣有讚有彈呢，因為多人講到佢隻狗公都上埋水同佢護航，講到乜都係佢送俾佢，佢份人唔係咁，15碎就送again B俾佢港女育成<br />\n7. 當時巴打整咗個社署舉報Template，當月數字係爆哂，社署有無做嘢就唔知<br />\n8. 蝗性難移，人哋話版權有問題，佢就自己去搶註，又話有send信去問任天堂<br />\n9. 假，明明自己搏上位，節目入面話好大壓力匿入衣櫃扮喊<br />\n10. 佢本身Jupas係派去嶺南，appeal咗先入得返KongU文學院<br />\n11. 中學果陣已經跟學校去美國，AL之後狗公陳強開個位佢做DJ都做做下走人去歐洲德國乜乜乜玩，雲海專欄寫咗文鬧爆要其他DJ執佢屎，大學期間秦國台灣乜乜乜唔洗講啦，外遊次數仲多過返工搵錢嘅連登仔<br />\n12. 15碎的夢話要做設計師乜乜嘛，自家設計帽呀嘛，果時又俾佢去天比高學嘢，KongU文學院！？選校花靠樣上位！？說好的Design呢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">資料由大陸偷食人妻絲打提供</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 鄭金鈴事蹟</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/002245_09bc58d9c38609c6ec5d8f2861d009b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F002245_09bc58d9c38609c6ec5d8f2861d009b3.png&h=f8b3f6db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呃綜援(見上圖 <br />\n15歲接受訪問時聲稱賣帽只係想減輕屋企負擔，但轉頭又問老母攞錢去美國<br />\n<br />\n為左上位中學已經溝個大自己十年既男人<br />\n成功比佢r到係903做dj 有自己一個鐘既節目<br />\n無責任心，一句要去成個月德國grad trip<br />\n就掉底個電台節目<br />\n<br />\n借助其他人黎幫自己上位，用完即棄<br />\n<br />\n攞完哂香港資源就閃人去泡國追星姣仔扮韓妹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當初貪walter kwan 有d錢就痴埋去 <br />\n同人拍緊拖仲同啲韓仔攬頭攬頸<br />\n後尾仲爲自己做beggar上左位好多選擇就飛尻人 完美演繹大陸西女人本性<br />\n<br />\n有女朋友既仔都姣，唔識避忌<br />\n<br />\n同成班男人一齊去滑雪住埋一齊飲哂酒知咩事啦<br />\n仲upload埋上youtube比全世界知佢有幾放蕩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賤貨疑似比帽水哥帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n經常係youtube封面加上某幾位韓星 <br />\n再係tile誤導人片段中有明星出現<br />\n借用韓星上位 呃觀眾點擊率<br />\n<br />\n態度囂張 自我中心 <br />\n囂張回應觀眾原來有人會唔識韓文<br />\n韓文錯漏百出 仲自稱韓國達人<br />\n歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3e537dfc7ad611dae0dba1c1840e36f692183de6","tid":547014,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/005433_03ad69ff6742a91717c6aec628be8ee4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F005433_03ad69ff6742a91717c6aec628be8ee4.png&h=2c0dc930&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/005434_7a0517fcff99ec80a1fb8e5336bc931c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F005434_7a0517fcff99ec80a1fb8e5336bc931c.png&h=4cc24474&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/005435_7a0517fcff99ec80a1fb8e5336bc931c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F005435_7a0517fcff99ec80a1fb8e5336bc931c.png&h=a4d5d4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/005436_d376319bd6d76883544eb9cda634b2c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F005436_d376319bd6d76883544eb9cda634b2c6.png&h=7d3e3985&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>仲有呢幾張未放上黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/083343_91fe86161e465a8e35282be006f4700a.png\" data-thumbnail-